{"tid":1635930,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人冇資格爭取民主自由","createTime":"2019-10-07T15:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T04:29:45.000Z","uid":56047,"like":13,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d906abc433f1eaa493edb5ec2927edf7d388172b","tid":1635930,"uid":56047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:47:26.000Z","msg":"其實黑警都已經去到殺人既地步 香港人仲唔識醒<br />\n仲以為遊行下 喊下口號 拉下手 裝下修就爭取到五大訴求？ 以為係極權政權底下爭取民主好似細路仔咁扭計 人地就會比你？<br />\n如果繼續用而家唔溫唔火既方法 只會爭取到坐監案底 身體傷害（例如冇左隻眼） 一個唔好彩比黑警捉你去新屋嶺 冇埋條命 <br />\n但係其實就算有人死 香港人都唔care 831之後都冇人話要黑警填命 我地香港人死左咁多人 都冇一隻狗死 林鄭班狗官都仲冇穿冇爛 仲小小事又話割蓆<br />\n香港人就好似一隻唔識痛既豬 慢慢比政府宰割"},{"pid":"0abd9b20d6eb075b054f29aeb70195efbd08b9e7","tid":1635930,"uid":322141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:48:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"987b444ae1570e97b6938a9989eb0058f39e6256","tid":1635930,"uid":47659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"星期五個個講到好嬲好難受<br />\n點知過三日返二,連罷工罷市都做唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCarrie:香港人真易解決"},{"pid":"3eebacf7fa5d21f71a8493f99a3dfc21ddf730e0","tid":1635930,"uid":279640,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:48:46.000Z","msg":"少批評，多建設。咁你有咩建議？"},{"pid":"d8beb9782cab7452ceaeaddda0ba48c5c6c954f0","tid":1635930,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>星期五個個講到好嬲好難受<br />\n點知過三日返<span style=\"color: red;\">工</span>,連罷工罷市都做唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/