事接觸到唔少反共既大陸人<br />\n當然佔比仲係好小 但文宣 好聲好氣交流 100個入面都會有1,2個慢慢明白"},{"pid":"c902d78211168966eb3489046b1c3f96d5dbcaf3","tid":1635930,"uid":74827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"987b444ae1570e97b6938a9989eb0058f39e6256","tid":1635930,"uid":47659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"星期五個個講到好嬲好難受<br />\n點知過三日返二,連罷工罷市都做唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCarrie:香港人真易解決"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:55:01.000Z","msg":"講真 無工會無集過談判權<br />\n做大公司明知會被清算<br />\n你敢唔敢？<br />\n我唔會太怪責香港人<br />\n生活未差到要個個揾命博<br />\n抗爭歷史都太短<br />\n開埠以來都無點見過血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依呢個局勢 sorry地講 除非你重現64 好難有大罷工<br />\n仲要一兩日既罷工係無用<br />\n你全港罷足一禮拜兩禮拜一個月就習大大都要跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1109360a79383ef3e1dbde5260aadc3cd0d4a6f3","tid":1635930,"uid":74827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c902d78211168966eb3489046b1c3f96d5dbcaf3","tid":1635930,"uid":74827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"987b444ae1570e97b6938a9989eb0058f39e6256","tid":1635930,"uid":47659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"星期五個個講到好嬲好難受<br />\n點知過三日返二,連罷工罷市都做唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCa